                    <p class="feature-description">You can easily update your existing products with straightforward and self-explained interface.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="text-center feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs fa-3x text-secondary feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="mt-3">Flexible Configuration</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Customize the system to fit your unique business needs and workflows.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
